title: Smart Korean-Inspired Tofu Bowls with Sesame-Roasted Veggie Jumble and Gochujang Mayo
description: This low-carb, low-cal tofu bowl hits all the notes of a classic Korean rice bowl, but with a lighter twist! Feel free to fry an egg and pop it on top for extra protein (we highly recommend it!).

